<br>
Lets look back at the history of the Game.<br>
<br>
Kunark - You had to be in a Uber guild to get into Veeshan's Peak because of Traks. Traks was VERY VERY hard to kill back then.<br>
--Today -- Traks is killed with a 6 man group.<br>
<br>
Velious - Tormax/Dain/Yelinak/AoW/NTOV - Again You had to be in a uberguild back then to kill these mobs.<br>
--Today -- All those mobs can be done with Three groups or less<br>
<br>
Luclin - Ssra (Emperor) - Was a freaking Monster. Same with a few other mobs in Ssra. Today he can be killed with 30 or less and isn't near the difficulty he once was.<br>
<br>
Planes of power - Today people are learning tactics to kill mobs. They are keeping tight lipped about it. Sooner or later people will let some secrets out (Always happens), and at that point other guilds will enter the elemental planes. <br>
<br>
My biggest point -- Not all guilds progress at the same rate. Sooner or later guild move up. Sooner or later you'll be able to get the items to do the quest above.<br>
<br>
When do you want to get your tradeskills up? Now or Whenever you can get the items? (Me personally I would have rather started doing tradeskills back in when kunark was release than to do it now)<br>
